  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Bolton\" title=\"House Bolton\"><img alt=\"House Bolton.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0c/House_Bolton.svg/50px-House_Bolton.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0c/House_Bolton.svg/75px-House_Bolton.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0c/House_Bolton.svg/100px-House_Bolton.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Belthasar Bolton</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Bolton\" title=\"House Bolton\"><img alt=\"House Bolton.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0c/House_Bolton.svg/50px-House_Bolton.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0c/House_Bolton.svg/75px-House_Bolton.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0c/House_Bolton.svg/100px-House_Bolton.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Bolton\" title=\"House Bolton\">House Bolton</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">Northmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Belthasar Bolton</b> was a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bolton\" title=\"House Bolton\">House Bolton</a> who participated in the <a href=\"/index.php/Rape_of_the_Three_Sisters\" title=\"Rape of the Three Sisters\">Rape of the Three Sisters</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Belthasar_Bolton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Chronicles_of_Longsister\" title=\"The Chronicles of Longsister\">The Chronicles of Longsister</a></i> state that during the <a href=\"/index.php/Rape_of_the_Three_Sisters\" title=\"Rape of the Three Sisters\">Rape of the Three Sisters</a> by the <a href=\"/index.php/Kings_of_Winter\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kings of Winter\">Kings of Winter</a>, Belthasar had a \"<a href=\"/index.php/Pink_Pavilion\" title=\"Pink Pavilion\">Pink Pavilion</a>\" made from the <a href=\"/index.php/Flaying\" title=\"Flaying\">flayed</a> skins of one hundred <a href=\"/index.php/Sistermen\" title=\"Sistermen\">Sistermen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Belthasar_Bolton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Vale.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403203422\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.074 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.270 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 473/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10424/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4592/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 318/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 849/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.44 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  259.789      1 -total\n 96.70%  251.227      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 95.91%  249.160      1 Template:Infobox\n 12.42%   32.259     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  4.04%   10.495      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.49%    6.480      2 Template:Ref\n  1.64%    4.250      2 Template:Ref/core\n  0.69%    1.797      1 Template:References\n  0.38%    0.993      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:18746-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403203422 and revision id 298869\n -->\n",
